  "golemDetails": "Umami Analytics syncs all website analytics data to Arkiv blockchain for backup and decentralization. Data includes pageviews, events, sessions, and website metadata. Uses smart annotations (type, source, website_id, timestamp) for efficient querying. BTL set to ~1,296,000 blocks (30 days) for automatic cleanup.",
